    - set_meta_tags site: 'Super 80s World', title: 'The retro-game of the decade... the 1980 s!', description: 'Super 80s World is the first retro-platformer set in the 1980s.  Fans of retrogaming & supporters of indie games will love the campy nostalgia of the decade.', keywords: %w[1980s game mobile indie retro retrogaming mario platformer synthwave ios android 80s nostalgia streets rage neon pixel 8bit fun development]

